      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TALKACHINO (7) racing well this campaign and ready for the 1400m in this stronger contest. Anchored with the 64kg at latest with a narrow third over 1300m at Dubbo in BM58 class. Gets in light and can stalk EPAULLO CREED. Go close. FUTURE FUND (5) back in trip and relished the heavy conditions with a solid on-pace victory over 1400m at Wagga. Jumps in weight but gets map favours today. Top-three player. EPAULLO CREED (2) has a good record at this trip and finds a weaker contest. Came out positive from the inside gate but was beaten a long way from home when he floundered in the going to finish sixth over 1600m at Wagga. Looking for a firmer surface and capable of better. RED BERYL (6) gets in light with the 3kg claim and can run into the minor money.",
